<item>
            <title>[LU-14770] sanity-selinux test_21b: client timeout</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14770</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for S Buisson &amp;lt;sbuisson@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/f7ad6fc3-18ed-4aaa-95e2-f09666fc0643&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/f7ad6fc3-18ed-4aaa-95e2-f09666fc0643&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_21b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Timeout occurred after 274 mins, last suite running was sanity-selinux
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On OSS side we can see messages complaining about request replays:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[12875.747152] LustreError: 265433:0:(sec_gss.c:504:gss_do_check_seq()) seq 1 (in main window) is a replay: max 1, winsize 2048
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;and checksum mismatch:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[12881.379209] LustreError: 265433:0:(gss_sk_mech.c:388:sk_verify_hmac()) checksum mismatch
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Finally the client gets evicted:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[13034.439160] Lustre: lustre-OST0002: haven&apos;t heard from client 33609750-dfdf-4cdb-b17a-cf79a49f7b31 (at 10.9.7.36@tcp) in 49 seconds. I think it&apos;s dead, and I am evicting it. exp 00000000e0bea176, cur 1623763560 expire 1623763530 last 1623763511
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;





&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity-selinux test_21b - Timeout occurred after 274 mins, last suite running was sanity-selinux&lt;/p&gt;</description>
